{"tid":1466050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和你飛 = 和理非","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:04.000Z","uid":88023,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"679453e4203c0a7bbaa135b08b5fdc0c9b24ad4c","tid":1466050,"uid":88023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:29:51.000Z","msg":"和你飛 講到明就係 和理非<br />\n一開始唔係講好左咩？和理非接力<br />\n<br />\n係機場開片，有事上黎點走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有鬼有點？由六月開始就有架啦，又如何<br />\n而家人地明顯就係用鬼黎令你亂，咁就有道理清場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後再去既冷靜少少<br />\n諗返起和你飛係和理非好無？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 做左就係做左，不割蓆但要有檢討<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Be humble"},{"pid":"28c923e2fbbda98edc00d4e7184bb61bf92ba3c3","tid":1466050,"uid":88023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:30:03.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"825e3fe14517a8d02374b67cc10bdefaf756c496","tid":1466050,"uid":88023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:30:19.000Z","msg":"十連無難度"},{"pid":"11d19634682e325c4524d2201a3236ae57e34652","tid":1466050,"uid":88023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99456268bc3f1879efc5a5d1ae5800371f7fb777","tid":1466050,"uid":88023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score